metadata.description: With the release of „Through the Portal“ I’m officially announcing the „Sound Circle“ - a series of 12 interconnected drops, each ending with a few bars from the following release. These musical cliffhangers create an interactive experience for the listener and provide a deeper understanding of how I’m re-contextualising musical ideas. For this release, the ending of my first sound.xyz drop „From Beyond“ makes a surprise appearance with a completely different vibe. Can you discover it?
metadata.name: Through the Portal - Golden Egg
metadata.title: Through the Portal
